Class EncoderTurn

java.lang.Object
  edu.wpi.first.wpilibj.command.Command
      storm2013.commands.EncoderTurn
All Implemented Interfaces:
NamedSendable, Sendable
public class EncoderTurn
extends Command

Same as EncoderDrive, but it turns rather than drive. We're not using it this year because encoders suck on skid-steer systems.

Author:
evan1026
